Hi guys! So here’s the saved love from today’s live with @prettyfitj! Girl intense! I’ve left the workout below if you want to try it out! 
Squat to press x15
Plank row to half burpee x10
Side lunge to curl x10e
Side shuffle x1 to burpee x5e side 
Plank hold jacks x20
Sit up to press then Russian twist x10

Complete 4 ROUNDS!
